to_finset_some:
@[simp]
theorem to_finset_some {a : α} : (some a).to_finset = {a} :=
  rfl
#align to_finset_some to_finset_some

@[simp]
theorem to_finset_none : none.to_finset = (∅ : Finset α) :=
  rfl
#align to_finset_none to_finset_none
some_mem_insert_none:
theorem some_mem_insert_none {s : Finset α} {a : α} : some a ∈ s.insert_none ↔ a ∈ s := by simp
#align some_mem_insert_none some_mem_insert_none
mem_to_finset:
@[simp]
theorem mem_to_finset {a : α} {o : option α} : a ∈ o.to_finset ↔ a ∈ o := by cases o <;> simp [eq_comm]
#align mem_to_finset mem_to_finset
mem_insert_none:
/-⟨none ::ₘ s.1.map some, multiset.nodup_cons.2
  ⟨by simp, s.nodup.map $ λ a b, option.some.inj⟩⟩-/
@[simp]
theorem mem_insert_none {s : Finset α} : ∀ {o : option α}, o ∈ s.insert_none ↔ ∀ a ∈ o, a ∈ s
  | none => iff_of_true (Multiset.mem_cons_self _ _) fun a h => by cases h
  | some a => Multiset.mem_cons.trans <| by simp <;> rfl
#align mem_insert_none mem_insert_none
mem_erase_none:
@[simp]
theorem mem_erase_none {s : Finset (option α)} {x : α} : x ∈ s.erase_none ↔ some x ∈ s := by simp [erase_none]
#align mem_erase_none mem_erase_none
map_some_erase_none:
@[simp]
theorem map_some_erase_none [decidable_eq (option α)] (s : Finset (option α)) :
    s.erase_none.map Embedding.some = s.erase none := by rw [map_eq_image, embedding.some_apply, image_some_erase_none]
#align map_some_erase_none map_some_erase_none
insert_none_erase_none:
@[simp]
theorem insert_none_erase_none [decidable_eq (option α)] (s : Finset (option α)) :
    insert_none (erase_none s) = insert none s := by ext (_ | x) <;> simp
#align insert_none_erase_none insert_none_erase_none
image_some_erase_none:
@[simp]
theorem image_some_erase_none [decidable_eq (option α)] (s : Finset (option α)) :
    s.erase_none.image some = s.erase none := by ext (_ | x) <;> simp
#align image_some_erase_none image_some_erase_none
erase_none_union:
@[simp]
theorem erase_none_union [decidable_eq (option α)] [decidable_eq α] (s t : Finset (option α)) :
    (s ∪ t).erase_none = s.erase_none ∪ t.erase_none := by
  ext
  simp
#align erase_none_union erase_none_union
erase_none_none:
@[simp]
theorem erase_none_none : ({none} : Finset (option α)).erase_none = ∅ :=
  by
  ext
  simp
#align erase_none_none erase_none_none
erase_none_map_some:
@[simp]
theorem erase_none_map_some (s : Finset α) : (s.map Embedding.some).erase_none = s :=
  by
  ext
  simp
#align erase_none_map_some erase_none_map_some
erase_none_inter:
@[simp]
theorem erase_none_inter [decidable_eq (option α)] [decidable_eq α] (s t : Finset (option α)) :
    (s ∩ t).erase_none = s.erase_none ∩ t.erase_none := by
  ext
  simp
#align erase_none_inter erase_none_inter
erase_none_insert_none:
@[simp]
theorem erase_none_insert_none (s : Finset α) : erase_none (insert_none s) = s :=
  by
  ext
  simp
#align erase_none_insert_none erase_none_insert_none
erase_none_image_some:
@[simp]
theorem erase_none_image_some [decidable_eq (option α)] (s : Finset α) : (s.image some).erase_none = s := by
  simpa only [map_eq_image] using erase_none_map_some s
#align erase_none_image_some erase_none_image_some
erase_none_eq_bUnion:
theorem erase_none_eq_bUnion [decidable_eq α] (s : Finset (option α)) : s.erase_none = s.bUnion option.to_finset :=
  by
  ext
  simp
#align erase_none_eq_bUnion erase_none_eq_bUnion
erase_none_empty:
@[simp]
theorem erase_none_empty : (∅ : Finset (option α)).erase_none = ∅ :=
  by
  ext
  simp
#align erase_none_empty erase_none_empty
coe_erase_none:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ⁻¹' » -/
@[simp]
theorem coe_erase_none (s : Finset (option α)) : (s.erase_none : set α) = «expr ⁻¹' » some s :=
  Set.ext fun x => mem_erase_none
#align coe_erase_none coe_erase_none
card_to_finset:
theorem card_to_finset (o : option α) : o.to_finset.card = o.elim 0 1 := by cases o <;> rfl
#align card_to_finset card_to_finset
card_insert_none:
@[simp]
theorem card_insert_none (s : Finset α) : s.insert_none.card = s.card + 1 := by simp [insert_none]
#align card_insert_none card_insert_none
